title: Apartment for Rent: VOC-kade 314
description: Large living room with open kitchen. Kitchen includes built-in appliances. Beautiful view over the water. Shared roof garden with beautiful views over Amsterdam.

importantInformation.viewings: Viewings are unfortunately not possible for this new construction project; You rent from floor plans and impressions.
importantInformation.externalStorage: There is no separate external storage room at the house.
importantInformation.garage: There is no garage in the residential project. If you want to park a car, you have to arrange a parking space yourself.
importantInformation.deliveryDate: Apartments will be delivered this July.

notes.text: big plus for the waterfront view
